/* JT[132] (CODE 6 + 0x0092) — set the current file-group id.
 *   g_a5_-31236 = (byte)id;
 * The group id (51 / 0x33 for GAME) tags subsequent file-cache
 * registrations; jt361 sets it before loading the GAME header. */
